					<h1>Company Overview</h1>
					<div class="main_content_body">
						<h4>
	<img alt="litigation support company" src="http://www.lorr.com/images/uploads/company2.jpg" style="float: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; width: 606px; height: 321px; "></h4>
<h4>
	You solve the puzzle. We gather the pieces.</h4>
<p>
	Law &amp; Order Record Retrieval and<b> Litigation Support</b> provides law firms and insurers with prompt, dependable, cost-effective services in cases throughout Texas. As a top <i>litigation support company</i> in the state of Texas we're here to work for you. So, call us when a claim or suit is filed, and we'll support you all the way to settlement or trial.</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		LORR supports your investigation with photographers and videographers to document site inspections, chronicle injuries and recovery, and create day-in-the-life videos.</li>
	<li>
		LORR supports your discovery by obtaining medical, business, and federal, state, and municipal agency records, then delivering them to you in print or digital format. We'll provide court reporters and videographers for depositions. Plus, we can scan your records and exhibits to make them securely accessible 24/7 via the Internet.</li>
	<li>
		LORR supports you at trial by preparing multimedia presentations, digital exhibit databases, and trial boards, and by serving witnesses with subpoenas. We also provide courtroom playback, dealing with the technology while you concentrate on your case.</li>
	<li>
		LORR supports your research with our free online resources.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	Whether you're an attorney, staff, or adjuster, Plaintiff or Defendant, let LORR gather the pieces of your case.</p>
